data.name: tbtn_TT_AllowCustomModules
data.value: Allows BLREdit to Adopt Modules in the Module Folder into the Installed Module List Client and Server are both set as Default to be Loaded

data.name: tbtn_TT_EnableAPI
data.value: Enables the App-Web-Protocol API. Important needs Admin priviliges to install the Protocol into the Windows Registry. Needs a Restart to Install Protocol!

data.name: tbtn_TT_ForceRuntimeCheck
data.value: Forces the Runtime Check Dialog to display

data.name: tbtn_TT_InstallRequiredModules
data.value: Installs all Required Modules just before launch

data.name: tbtn_TT_RuntimeCheck
data.value: Checks if all necessary MVC++ Runtimes are installed to make the Gamework only needed when the game was not installed via Steam

data.name: tbtn_TT_ServerWatchDog
data.value: Enables the Server WatchDog which will Restart's the server instantly if it crashes or get's closed while BLRedit is Runnning!

data.name: tbtn_TT_ShowUpdateNotice
data.value: Opens the default Web browser to the Newest release when a new one is available
